name: Web 3 Innovation Lab
description: The Web3 Innovation Lab represents the future of decentralized innovation and is safeguarded by the Innovation DAO’s NFT. By tokenizing our video, we anchor it on the blockchain, protecting our intellectual property as inventors. As part of the Legacy NFT Collection, this token preserves our original concept and secures it for generations to come. The video showcases our vision of a Web3 Purpose Economy, where gamification, community governance, and tokenized incentives drive innovation and promote economic inclusion—all while establishing a comprehensive business model for a self-sustaining, financially viable DAO.
